response.overview: On December 06, 2017, Sasebo General Ground Gymnasium in Sasebo, Nagasaki, Japan hosted Day 15 of NJPW World Tag League 2017.  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Beretta, Gedo, Kazuchika Okada & Will Ospreay).  The card also featured CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada, Will Ospreay & Gedo) vs Los Ingobernables de Japon (EVIL & SANADA).  Other wrestlers on the show include Tomohiro Ishii, Toru Yano, and Davey Boy Smith Jr., and more!
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017: Day 15
